  <brief_title>Is NIRS Able to Detect Ischemia Following Brain Insult</brief_title>
  <acronym>NIRS</acronym>
  <official_title>The New 4 Wavelengths EQUANOX NIRS Sensor: Correlation and Detection of Ischemic Episodes. An Observational Comparative Study Versus PtiO2</official_title>
  <sponsors>
